        </item>
        <item>
            <title>动物森友会 x LEGO 新产品登场　两款场景包括服务处和机场</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 15:00:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[LEGO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[动物森友会]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231847</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《动物森友会》几年前曾经相当热门，至今仍然有不少玩家。LEGO 在上月推出联乘产品，最近再次公布新作，包含两款人气游戏场景。<br /><span id="more-1231847"></span></p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">🎵 K.K. is bringing some extra groove to the LEGO Animal Crossing range from August 1! <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/LEGO?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#LEGO</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/AnimalCrossing?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#AnimalCrossing</a><a href="https://t.co/R2uIW9lDIa">pic.twitter.com/R2uIW9lDIa</a></p><p>&mdash; LEGO (@LEGO_Group) <a href="https://twitter.com/LEGO_Group/status/1783858761444037049?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 26, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>LEGO 在 X 上公布，将会在 8 月 1 日推出新的《动物森友会》场景套装，包括有服务处和 Dodo 机场两款，前者除了建筑物之外，还会有小火车、美食摊以及 K.K. 演唱会舞台。组合中除了 K.K. 外还会有西施惠和莫妮卡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingto-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231848" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingto-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingto.jpg 791w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>至于机场套装，则会有水上飞机和沙滩摆设，人物方面有陆德里和纯纯。不过暂时仍然未有例如套装的实际积木数量以及价格等详情，有兴趣的朋友可以继续留意一下。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingda-694x367.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="367" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231849" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingda-694x367.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/legoanimalcrossingda.jpg 854w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://jaysbrickblog.com/news/two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming-in-august-2024-including-a-kk-slider-minifigure/">Jay&#8217;s Brick Blog</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/two-more-lego-animal-crossing-sets-coming/game-channel/">动物森友会 x LEGO 新产品登场　两款场景包括服务处和机场</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
